Bucket Policy (Best Practice)

S3 Console
→ Your Bucket
→ Permissions tab
→ Bucket Policy
→ Edit
→ Paste this policy:

{
  "Version": "2012-10-17",
  "Statement": [
    {
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Principal": "*",
      "Action": "s3:GetObject",
      "Resource": "arn:aws:s3:::my-bucket/*"
