Step 1: Enable ACL on Bucket (Object Ownership)

S3 Console
→ Your Bucket
→ Permissions tab
→ Object Ownership
→ Edit
→ Select: ACLs enabled
→ Select: Bucket owner preferred
→ Check the confirmation checkbox
→ Save changes ✅

Step 2: Turn Off Block Public Access

S3 Console
→ Your Bucket
→ Permissions tab
→ Block public access (bucket settings)
→ Edit
→ Uncheck: Block all public access ✅
→ Save changes
→ Type "confirm"
→ Confirm ✅

